description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Yulenka purrs with a rating of 33, and a multiplier of 8x. It has a total score of 264, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, 8 for East, Leverage for South, and 3 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80338-38634-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [264 Votes, Top 5% Score]
